For women’s month I wanted to speak to and with other women about the importance of our health ♥️ 
Spiritual, mental, physical, and sexual health are just some of the ways in which we can show ourselves love and respect.

We should ALL be prioritizing our health for the sake of ourselves, our families, and our communities!!! 

As women, we also have reasons to take HIV prevention seriously. @viivhealthcare has created workbooks to help us communicate with each other, our partners & with our health care providers. Check the link in my stories to download 🔗 #risktoreasons
